description: These cinnamon rolls get much of their sweetness naturally from pumpkin puree and honey.
name: Pumpkin Cinnamon Rolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Mix the cream cheese, 1/2 a tsp of cinnamon and 2 tbs of honey together to make a glaze. Spread the glaze on the warm buns and serve.
